oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Claude King and Rex Allen Jr. (masking sheet)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Allen, Rex, 1947-; King, Claude, 1923-2013; Moeller Talent, Inc.; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising fantastic entertainment featuring Claude King and Rex Allen, Jr., available for exclusive bookings through Moeller Talent, Inc. The negatives feature photographs of Claude King and Rex Allen, Jr., and would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
